data.name: Index_Content_Main
data.value:
What is the project "Matta Sur-connect with memory"?

Matta Sur Conecta is a project carried out by different students of the University of Boyacá-Tunja that their only objective is to provide a perfect place for any entity that wants it, the initiative of this project is to make known the patrimony Cultural of Matta Sur in Santiago de Chile, Siguiente to the asylum and the building of a new recreational park is to become one of the best patrimonial places that exist.

data.name: Topic_1
data.value:
What do we do?

We elaborate, design and construct architectural plans for the internal and external improvement of the asylum of the poor, making it the best recreational park of all.

data.name: Topic_2
data.value:
Using TIC

We use information and communication technologies to make known the process carried out throughout the construction of this project, in the same way, a mobile application is used which allows to provide facilid Ad to the user regarding the guide and location of everything you want inside the park.

data.name: Topic_3

Growing your experience and experiences

In and out of the former asylum Sisters of the Poor, you can live one of your best moments, because, along with the visual experience and entertainment that the Park offers by Web-Mobile application you can have one of the best moments of your life.
